{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"75d60e588b","title":"国务院关于禁止私自放映封存影片的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3f4759ca23","index":0,"year":1973,"month":11,"day":26,"articleId":"75d60e588b","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"文学艺术","id":"5387dec24b","type":"主题"},{"name":"文化宗教和社会生活","id":"6d08cec53d","type":"主题"},{"name":"国务院文件","id":"c0a0ee982d","type":"发行机构"},{"name":"中央文件","id":"ef6e778547","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fc92847fc3","type":"title","text":"国务院关于禁止私自放映封存影片的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d60e588b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"05e8227620","type":"paragraph","text":"国务院关于禁止私自放映封存影片的通知","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d60e588b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e1d11ff062","type":"paragraph","text":"1973.11.26；国发 ［1973］165号","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d60e588b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f5ce421c00","type":"paragraph","text":"各省、市、自治区革命委员会，国务院各部委：","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d60e588b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c769fdd677","type":"paragraph","text":"近来，有些地区和部门未经中央批准私自放映封存影片而且看的范围很广，这是违反中央规定的。中央有些部门，在京召开的专业会议，看内部参考影片，范围过火，看后也不组织批判消毒。这个问题，各地区，各部门，应当引起重视，严肃对待。今后，对封存的影片，必须严格管理，对经批准放映的内部参考影片，必须严格控制放映范围。为此，特作如下通知：","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d60e588b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6226f02d77","type":"paragraph","text":"一、必须坚决贯彻执行中共中央一九六八年六十号文件的规定。凡封存的影片，未经中央批准，一律不得动用。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d60e588b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"30ec1b4f27","type":"paragraph","text":"二、看内部参考影片按下列规定办理 ：","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d60e588b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0a98f169b4","type":"paragraph","text":"1、凡是国务院已批准放映的内部参考影片，可组织内部放映。放映范围，应按国务院一九七—年十四号文件的规定严格执行。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d60e588b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1e7a784c3b","type":"paragraph","text":"中央各部门看上述影片，可持部委领导同志签署的函件，到“中影公司”租、借影片。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d60e588b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"13e989b6ee","type":"paragraph","text":"2、中宣部、外交部、总参二部以及新闻文艺、科研等单位组织观看内部参考影片，需列出片名，报请中央领导同意后，持批件到“中影公司”租借影片。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d60e588b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"65c62a50a2","type":"paragraph","text":"3、外宾看内部参考影片，由有关外事部门报请中央领导同志批准后，持批件到“中影公司”租、借影片。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d60e588b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c271c33274","type":"paragraph","text":"4、各地区、各部门看了内部参考影片，必须组织批判。毒草经过锄掉，才能化为肥料。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d60e588b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"302cc622d0","type":"paragraph","text":"以上希遵照执行。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d60e588b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a455df4521","type":"paragraph","text":"（此件可发至县，由省、市，自治区革委会自行印发）","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75d60e588b","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}